{"id": 1876, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于餐厅菜单，你有哪些不能忍的点？", "description": "哪些有关菜单的花头或者创新，你并不会买账？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 24816, "comment_count": 22, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170828165741ewjqa1cgvZNiLu0p.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-08-30T17:00:40Z", "questions": [{"id": 2867, "title": "关于餐厅菜单，你有哪些不能忍的点？", "content": "关于餐厅菜单，你有哪些不能忍的点？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 232020, "content": "假装有网感和亲切感，非要叫“西红柿爱上鸡蛋”什么的", "image": "img/option/option/201708291140314XZY6zuwPpSf7iBA.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232231, "content": "诡异的武侠风格和江湖气息，黯然销魂饭，十全大补丸，不知道具体菜是啥", "image": "img/option/option/20170830171217KohIiFykVEmaXTBZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232243, "content": "排列凌乱，前面是“十大推荐菜”“新菜”，后面又按不同分类重新出现一遍", "image": "img/option/option/20170829124203mCKf5sjkp6nSBOe8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232244, "content": "菜品推荐分类特别多，“主厨推荐\"\"本店推荐”“招牌菜”，分不清楚谁是谁", "image": "img/option/option/20170829124145oauBfnHjzCtm7ZiL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232245, "content": "炒作“隐藏菜单”，但其实就是把不同菜或者饮品的原料排列组合", "image": "img/option/option/20170829142634Kv6E9ice8tl5hyHV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232246, "content": "一定要写上漏洞百出的英文翻译，感觉外国人根本看不懂", "image": "img/option/option/20170829125916T5CKvs3zVLnxrpHh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232247, "content": "没有图片也不注明分量，只能偷瞄邻桌来判断该点多少", "image": "img/option/option/20170829125254URwpHfIXBnrtukWG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232248, "content": "套餐的配菜没说明，一份汉堡里面明明包括不少薯条结果又点了一大份薯条", "image": "img/option/option/20170829124444gCpXfSjr4hOnq9tl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232249, "content": "同个餐厅在不同外卖平台上菜品图片不一样", "image": "img/option/option/20170829130531Y97VGDECQw5J1ycl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 232638, "content": "完全不同的餐厅在外卖平台上用同一套图片", "image": "img/option/option/20170830171716rtGZMH2nQqUKNaSm.jpeg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}